                <solution>
                    <p>The first step is always to find the slope between our points: <m>(\overset{x_1}{-3},\overset{y_1}{150})</m> and <m>(\overset{x_2}{0},\overset{y_2}{30})</m>. Using the <xref ref="equation-slope-formula" text="title">slope formula</xref>, we have:
